data.description:
Welcome home to your cozy ranch style townhome in South City Park! This charming two bedroom home is the perfect spot to entertain your friends in your large living room, or host a bbq in your beautiful backyard! This home boasts gorgeous hardwood floors, a recently updated kitchen and is a corner unit with great lighting. With a 2 car garage + extra storage in the basement for all your gear, you're free to savor everything you love about living in both Denver and Colorado. 

This adorable home is in the perfect location! With handcrafted cocktails, coffee shops, award-winning restaurants  + music venues in the nearby Bluebird District to insta-perfect sunsets at City Park, all just blocks away. You are going to LOVE living here!
